p: In the GC-MS analysis of the essential oil of T. procumbens, it was possible to identify 20 compounds divided between sesquiterpenes and oxygenated terpenes, according to Table 1. Among the major compounds of T. procumbens oil, thymol (48.22%), Î³-terpinene (15.93%), and o-cymene (10.27%) are the most important.
